{"tid":40979,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"哈佛講師試畀你睇 用一湯匙橄欖油令湖面平靜","createTime":"2016-12-15T14:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-15T14:31:19.000Z","uid":22736,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d1a99e7c24a4991df17ef4387fd21b6fc7494f14","tid":40979,"uid":22736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:11:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161215&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56049477\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161215%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56049477&d=CQ6U9pJmG1NypnZ2%2BLCg%2BYscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=72f7770a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fs.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fa.php%3Fi%3D20161215%26s%3D10793140%26a%3D56049477&h=33413525\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://s.nextmedia.com/realtime/a.php?i=20161215&amp;s=10793140&amp;a=56049477</a><br />\n玩水上活動又怕暈船浪？這個方法可能幫到你。美國哈佛大學一名講師示範只需要一湯匙橄欖油，數分鐘內便可以令湖面「風平浪靜」。<br />\n哈佛大學物理講師凱斯廷（Greg Kestin）為了令實驗效果更明顯，他親身上陣泛舟湖上，把一湯匙橄欖油倒進湖中。從片中可見，湖面起初翻起一波波小浪，但當他把油倒入湖後，皮艇周邊的湖面開始平靜，數分鐘後，橄欖油在水面上散開，約半英畝（2,023平方米）的湖面頓變「波平如鏡」。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2016/12/15/221109_af9bae3c84b1c9588865a770bb4e7d53.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2016%2F12%2F15%2F221109_af9bae3c84b1c9588865a770bb4e7d53.jpg&h=c9e1a2fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53f3a9e223b8f49d346eaad1e167528766dc0631","tid":40979,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:12:40.000Z","msg":"文科仔唔識嘢<br />\n有冇巴打可以解釋下？"},{"pid":"bde30638cb034d1fe90d16e49117062be26ddb26","tid":40979,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:19:48.000Z","msg":"有沒有巴絲可以講解下個原理"},{"pid":"c7a6df666be2d309fd510598e22dc23ba96ba914","tid":40979,"uid":8557,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:22:04.000Z","msg":"得果個area平靜有咩用"},{"pid":"7aec73e51df881c038ecd2fa724730e581fcc5a7","tid":40979,"uid":24696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:23:27.000Z","msg":"他解釋，當橄欖油倒入湖水後，油分子帶負電荷的一方會被水分子帶正電荷的一方吸引，因此油分子會在湖面平均擴散，形成一層僅1粒分子厚的薄膜，「如同在湖面鋪上一塊不容易打摺的地毯，風吹過後，湖面也不會翻浪」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"05e6b936f89b3f4106ccebc4ff5761c462674d48","tid":40979,"uid":43189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:26:14.000Z","msg":"唔係水溝油溝唔埋既原理？"},{"pid":"7896df0e1847ed9c4fc7c286fa16dcb631af6f3d","tid":40979,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-15T14:31:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>他解釋，當橄欖油倒入湖水後，油分子帶負電荷的一方會被水分子帶正電荷的一方吸引，因此油分子會在湖面平均擴散，形成一層僅1粒分子厚的薄膜，「如同在湖面鋪上一塊不容易打摺的地毯，風吹過後，湖面也不會翻浪」。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nOk<br />\n冇click入去睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}